snippet.title: BREAKING: Car runs off the range road
snippet.content:
A CAR has reportedly run off the road at the Eton Range about 50km east of Nebo.
According to QAS, it's been reported as a single vehicle running off the road.
There are four QFES crews heading to the scene.
